_:N90bb6404df2c460897014cbce092bd97 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Baroness Sherlock OBE was appointed as a Minister of State in the Department for Work and Pensions on 17 December 2024. She was previously Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State at the Department of Work and Pensions from 9 July 2024 to 17 December 2024.</p>\n" .
